Title:Cart Empties on Logout

Description:When logging out of an account, 
any items in the cart will have been removed when logging back in.

The minimal steps necessary to reproduce:Log into an account, 
place any item into the cart, log off of account, 
log back onto the same account, open cart.

Environment: Microsoft Edge

Expected results:Items placed into cart to be retained between logins.

Assigned to: Andre Baptiste
Severity: Minor